Paper: hep-th/9711119

Date: 1997-11-17

Title: Alternative Solution of the Path Integral for the Radial Coulomb Problem

Authors: C.Grosche

Comments: 7 pages, Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Scripta 57 (1998) 609-611

In this Letter I present an alternative solution of the path integral for theradial Coulomb problem which is based on a two-dimensional singular version ofthe Levi-Civita transformation.